text.section:
The Newsprint Recycling Task Force shall meet as necessary to monitor the use of newsprint in the state for the following goals:
To increase the demand for recycled newsprint in Kentucky;
To increase the availability for the product;
To establish Kentucky as a reliable source of old newsprint for recycling; and
To identify, develop, and advance initiatives to recycle and reuse discarded newspapers and paper products with an emphasis on recycling these materials instead of diverting them for disposal.
